{"tid":2252643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"基斯柏特因唔撐拜登遭網民狙擊 羅拔唐尼出聲護航","createTime":"2020-10-21T15:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T15:09:12.000Z","uid":258948,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9700cbb4fd23f531380b2fea6098484ef406bd","tid":2252643,"uid":258948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:06:39.000Z","msg":"Sauce: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201021/346PO46RMZBFZMMDEC7DS2GLMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201021%2F346PO46RMZBFZMMDEC7DS2GLMU%2F&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPer6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=503afa32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201021%2F346PO46RMZBFZMMDEC7DS2GLMU%2F&h=981941f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201021/346PO46RMZBFZMMDEC7DS2GLMU/</a><br />\n<br />\n//「星爵」基斯柏特（Chris Pratt）近日慘遭美國網民狙擊，話說一位電影人 Amy Berg於Twitter貼出影壇4個Chris，包括基斯柏特、「雷神」基斯咸斯禾夫（Chris Hemsworth）、基斯派克（Chris Pine）與「美國隊長」基斯伊雲斯（Chris Evans）的相片，並表示：「其中一個要走。」結果就引發網民熱烈討論，不少人都表示基斯柏特要走，因為他沒有公開表示支持哪一名總統，也未有跟隨其他Marvel英雄齊齊撐拜登，於是就被屈成特朗普支持者。加上他之前曾支持一間教會，而該教會又被指反LGBTQ，所以網民都稱他為「最差的荷李活Chris」。//<br />\n<br />\n完美示範左膠真係惡過共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df78b510b99b6680cf20d1e99a38436f2cfa413a","tid":2252643,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:09:12.000Z","msg":"為咗要達到政治目的 對付佢哋眼中嘅階級敵人就必然會先將佢搞臭"}]}